---
---

<section class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center bg-[#1a3317] overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background image -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat pointer-events-none" style="background-image: url('/images/hero.png');"></div>
  <!-- Dark overlay to keep text legible -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#1a3317]/70 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="mb-6" data-aos="fade-up">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-innovation-light text-innovation text-sm font-semibold">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-innovation animate-pulse"></span>
        ✦ Ahora también: Digestato de purín
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- H1 -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6 max-w-4xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
      Gestión integral de purines.
      <span class="block text-blue-accent">Eficiente, legal y sostenible.</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subtitle -->
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/85 max-w-2xl mb-10 leading-relaxed" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
      Desde 2016 ayudamos a ganaderos y agricultores de Aragón y Navarra a gestionar sus deyecciones porcinas con rigor técnico y cobertura total.
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
      <a
        href="/servicios"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-accent text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-accent/90 transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl text-base"
      >
        Ver nuestros servicios
      </a>
      <a
        href="/trabaja-con-nosotros"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-green-primary transition-all duration-200 text-base"
      >
        Únete al equipo →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
